_:N02946f20a3a14b6abed22a635ade72fd <http://schema.org/description> "NPL is the UK’s national metrology institute, providing the measurement capability that underpins the UK’s prosperity and quality of life. NPL is a public corporation of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ." .
